  "title": "Outdoor Sales (Skills Development Advisor / Roadshow)",
  "description": "<p>Join OOM Institute as a<strong> Sales Executive (Roadshows) </strong>and play a pivotal role in promoting our digital marketing training courses! 🚀 Engage with individuals, driving sales and help them enhance their skills through tailored learning programs. You’ll be involved in everything from roadshows to seminars, representing our brand with professionalism and energy.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p><ul><li><strong>5-Day Work Week</strong> – (4 weekdays & 1 weekend is required / 11am - 8pm)</li><li><strong>Competitive Salary & Benefits: </strong>High Base + High Coms + Attractive Incentive <strong>(Gross salary up to $7,000 to $10,000) </strong></li><li><strong>Flexi-Cash Benefits</strong>: Use for air tickets, accommodation, dental, medical, and more</li><li><strong>Leave Entitlements</strong>: Start with 14 days Annual Leave + 1 Birthday Leave</li></ul><p><strong></strong><br /><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>As part of our <strong>Roadshow Sales Team</strong>, you’ll:</p><ul><li>Engage potential clients and promote our digital marketing courses.</li><li>Offer tailored consultations to understand their career development needs.</li><li>Recommend the perfect courses to match their goals.</li><li>Handle the enrolment process from start to finish, ensuring a seamless journey for our clients.</li></ul><h3><strong>Skills & Qualifications:</strong></h3><ul><li>A friendly, outgoing personality with a passion for sales and people.<br /></li></ul>",
