    "description": "<p>Established since 2006, OOm is a continuously advancing, high growth, full-suite digital marketing agency, harbouring the mission to help companies conquer the digital landscape. Apart from achieving the official Premier Partner for Google and Meta (Facebook), our ranking as the top 3% of Google Partners in Singapore demonstrates our capabilities and successful endeavours as industry leaders.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Ambitious, zealous and driven, our desire for greatness expands beyond Singapore. We have made our mark in the Philippines, China and Hong Kong as well, accommodating growing digital demands with our data-driven strategies and proven results.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At OOm, people are our most valuable asset. That is why we advocate career development and growth. From attending trainings from Google, Meta (Facebook) and more, we believe in constantly upgrading your skills and inculcating lifelong learning that will keep you relevant no matter the circumstances. If you’re seeking a career that recognises talent and unleashes your potential, OOm is where you’ll fit right in.</p>",
